'''''Sleeth''''' was one of many [[Speeder/Legends|speeders]] used by one of the [[Sith Lord/Legends|Sith Lords]] fighting in the [[Battle of Mizra]]. It was named after the [[Sleeth]] creature which, apparently, described the Lord who rode it into combat.

